---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro'
import BlockHeader from '@components/BlockHeader.astro'
import siteConfig from '../site.config'
---

<Layout title={`About | ${siteConfig.title}`}>
  <BlockHeader>About</BlockHeader>
  
  <div class="prose max-w-none">
    <p>
      Hi there! I'm <strong>Rahul</strong>, a passionate developer who loves exploring the intricacies of code and technology.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      Welcome to <strong>wrapcode</strong> - my corner of the internet where I share insights about programming, 
      development techniques, and the ever-evolving world of technology. Here you'll find posts covering various 
      topics from web development and system design to programming concepts and tools that make our lives easier.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      When I'm not writing code or blog posts, you can find me exploring new technologies, contributing to open 
      source projects, or diving deep into the latest programming paradigms. I believe in learning by sharing, 
      and this blog is my way of giving back to the developer community.
    </p>
    
    <h2>What you'll find here</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Programming tutorials and guides</li>
      <li>Technology insights and analysis</li>
      <li>Development best practices</li>
      <li>Open source project discussions</li>
      <li>Personal reflections on the tech industry</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>Get in touch</h2>
    <p>
      Feel free to reach out if you want to discuss technology, collaborate on projects, or just say hello!
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>GitHub:</strong> <a href="https://github.com/r4hulp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@r4hulp</a></li>
      <li><strong>Twitter:</strong> <a href="https://twitter.com/_rahulpp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@_rahulpp</a></li>
      <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:0x1@duck.com">0x1@duck.com</a></li>
    </ul>
    
    <p>
      Thanks for stopping by, and I hope you find something useful here!
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose {
    @apply text-foreground leading-relaxed;
  }
  
  .prose p {
    @apply mb-4;
  }
  
  .prose h2 {
    @apply text-h2 font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-xl;
  }
  
  .prose ul {
    @apply ml-6 mb-4;
  }
  
  .prose li {
    @apply mb-2 list-disc text-li;
  }
  
  .prose a {
    @apply text-a hover:underline;
  }
  
  .prose strong {
    @apply font-semibold;
  }
</style>